  "about": {
    "headline": "Welcome to Cafe of India",
    "description": "Nestled in the charming town of Maynard, Massachusetts, Cafe of India brings you the rich and diverse flavors of authentic Indian cuisine. Our chefs use traditional recipes passed down through generations, combined with the freshest ingredients, to create dishes that delight every palate. Whether you're a longtime lover of Indian food or trying it for the first time, our warm and inviting atmosphere makes every visit a memorable experience.",
